	<article id="post-3738" class="post-3738 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-afghanistan category-civil-liberties category-current-affairs category-drugs-2 category-intelligence category-media category-nsa category-privacy-2 category-rttv category-snowden category-spies category-surveillance category-whistleblowers category-wikileaks tag-afghanistan tag-edward-snowden tag-glenn-greenwald tag-intelligence-2 tag-media-2 tag-nsa-privacy tag-surveillance-2 tag-whistleblowers-2 tag-wikileaks">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/05/whistleblowers-deserve-full-coverage-rt-interview.html" title="Permalink to Whistleblowers deserve full coverage" rel="bookmark">Whistleblowers deserve full coverage</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/05/whistleblowers-deserve-full-coverage-rt-interview.html" title="19:26" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-05-23T19:26:26+00:00" pubdate>May 23, 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/05/whistleblowers-deserve-full-coverage-rt-interview.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Here is my recent <span class="caps">RT</span> inter­view about the recent dis­pute between Wikileaks and Glenn Gre­en­wald on what exactly the para­met­ers should be in media report­ing of whis­tleblower disclosures:</p>
<p><img src="http://anniemachon.ch/wp-content/uploads/whistleblowers.jpg" alt="whistleblowers" width="710" height="397" class="placeholder alignleft size-full wp-image-3821" data-source="vimeo" data-id="96068681" /></p>
<p><a href="http://vimeo.com/96068681">Whis­tleblowers deserve full cov­er­age — <span class="caps">RT</span> inter­view</a> from <a href="http://vimeo.com/anniemachon">Annie Machon</a> on <a href="https://vimeo.com">Vimeo</a>.</p>
<p>Of course, thanks to Wikileaks <a href="http://wikileaks.org/WikiLeaks-statement-on-the-mass.html">this even­ing</a>, we now know the coun­try that Glenn Gre­en­wald redac­ted from his <a href="https://firstlook.org/theintercept/article/2014/05/19/data-pirates-caribbean-nsa-recording-every-cell-phone-call-bahamas/">ori­ginal report</a> was Afghanistan.</p>
<p>Why on earth should the Afgh­anis not be allowed to know the sheer scale of sur­veil­lance they live under? In fact, would many be sur­prised? This is an <a href="https://medium.com/@mensoh/1fe0ff093cdf">excel­lent related art­icle</a>, do read.</p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
