		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/01/ccc-talk-four-wars.html" title="Permalink to CCC talk — the Four Wars" rel="bookmark"><span class="caps">CCC</span> talk — the Four Wars</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/01/ccc-talk-four-wars.html" title="11:55" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-01-01T11:55:52+00:00" pubdate>January 1, 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2014/01/ccc-talk-four-wars.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>Here is my recent talk at the <span class="caps">CCC</span> in Ham­burg, dis­cuss­ing the war on ter­ror, the war on drugs, the war in the inter­net and the war on whis­tleblowers:<br />
<iframe src="//player.vimeo.com/video/83256212" height="281" width="500" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>
<p><a href="http://vimeo.com/83256212"><span class="caps">30C3</span> — The Four Wars; Ter­ror, whis­tleblowers, drugs, inter­net</a> from <a href="http://vimeo.com/anniemachon">Annie Machon</a> on <a href="https://vimeo.com">Vimeo</a>.</p>
