						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/05/rt-artile-about-mi6s-afghan-ghost-money.html" title="Permalink to RT article about MI6’s Afghan “ghost money”" rel="bookmark"><span class="caps">RT</span> article about <span class="caps">MI6</span>’s Afghan “ghost money”</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/05/rt-artile-about-mi6s-afghan-ghost-money.html" title="14:39" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-05-07T14:39:16+00:00" pubdate>May 7, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
