	<article id="post-2047" class="post-2047 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-acta category-big-brother category-civil-liberties category-current-affairs category-democracy category-drugs-2 category-economics category-extradition category-intelligence category-ip category-law category-leap category-mi5 category-nsa category-politics category-spies category-tv category-whistleblowers tag-aaron-swartz tag-annie-machon tag-civil-liberties-2 tag-copyright tag-corporatism tag-extradition-2 tag-fascism tag-intelligence-2 tag-internet tag-ip tag-kim-domcom tag-leap tag-max-keiser tag-mi5 tag-rt tag-spies-2 tag-the-keiser-report tag-war-on-drugs tag-war-on-terror">
		<header class="entry-header">
						<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/01/the-keiser-report-my-recent-interview.html" title="Permalink to The Keiser Report — my recent interview" rel="bookmark">The Keiser Report — my recent interview</a></h1>
			
						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/01/the-keiser-report-my-recent-interview.html" title="23:05" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2013-01-22T23:05:36+00:00" pubdate>January 22, 2013</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><span class="byauthor">Annie Machon</span></span></span><br>
                                <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/01/the-keiser-report-my-recent-interview.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a>
                                <br>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
		</header><!-- .entry-header -->

				<div class="entry-content">
			<p>My recent inter­view on Max Keiser’s excel­lent <a href="http://rt.com/"><span class="caps">RT</span></a> show, <a href="http://maxkeiser.com/"><em>The Keiser Report</em></a>, appar­ently now the <a href="http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/max-keiser-barack-obama-is-clueless-mitt-romney-will-bankrupt-the-country-8269633.html?action=gallery">most watched</a> Eng­lish lan­guage news com­ment­ary show across the world.</p>
<p>We were dis­cuss­ing such happy sub­jects as the war on ter­ror, the war on drugs, but pre­dom­in­antly the war on the internet:</p>
<p><iframe src="http://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/zlD8f7VEzxQ" height="315" width="560" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>
					</div><!-- .entry-content -->
		
		<footer class="entry-meta">
                        <a href="#" onclick="javascript:copyToClipboard('http://anniemachon.ch/annie_machon/2013/01/the-keiser-report-my-recent-interview.html')">Copy permalink to clipboard</a> &#8195;| &#8195;<a href="http://anniemachon.ch/privacy">Why no sharings links?</a><br>
												<span class="cat-links">
